Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with point-set registration, which is a common problem in computer vision. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the registration of articulated and deformable objects, which is relevant to robotics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper uses the EM algorithm for maximum likelihood estimation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with probabilistic methods for point-set registration. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as point-set registration is also relevant to computer graphics.
